    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
}

/* Sidebar Styling */
.sidebar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    right: -300px; /* Initially hidden off-screen */
    height: 100%;
    width: 300px;
    background-color: rgba(230, 140, 20, 0.95); /* Slightly less transparent */
    color: var(--header-text-white);
    box-shadow: -2px 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    transition: right 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1700;
    padding: 20px;
    overflow-y: auto;
}

/* Sidebar Menu Styles */
.sidebar nav {
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    margin-top: 60px; /* Adjust for spacing */
}

.sidebar-menu {
    list-style: none; /* Remove bullets */
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
}

.sidebar-menu li {
    margin-bottom: 8px; /* Space between items */
}

.sidebar-menu li a {
    color: var(--header-text-very-light-gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    display: block;
    padding: 4px 0; /* Clickable area */
}

.sidebar-menu li a:hover {
    color: var(--header-text-white); /* Hover effect */
    font-weight: bold;
}

.sidebar-menu ul {
    list-style: none; /* Remove bullets for sub-items */
    margin-left: 40px; /* Indentation */
    padding: 0;
}

.sidebar-menu ul li {
    margin-bottom: 4px; /* Space between sub-items */
}

.sidebar-menu ul li a {
    color: var(--header-text-light-gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding: 2px 0; /* Clickable area */
}

.sidebar-menu ul li a:hover {
    color: var(--header-text-white); /* Hover effect */
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Close Button Styling */
.sidebar .close-btn {
    position: absolute;
    text-decoration: none;
    top: 10px;
    right: 20px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--header-text-light-gray);
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 2000; /* Above other elements */
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.sidebar .close-btn:hover {
    color: var(--header-text-white); /* Hover effect */
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
}

/* Checkbox to toggle sidebar */
.toggle-sidebar {
    display: none;
}

/* Show sidebar when checkbox is checked */
.toggle-sidebar:checked ~ .sidebar {
    right: 0;
}

/* Overlay Effect */
.toggle-sidebar:checked ~ .overlay {
    display: block;
    opacity: 1; /* Fade in */
    pointer-events: auto;
}

/* Desktop Navigation Styling */
.desktop-only {
    display: block;
}

.desktop-only ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
}

.desktop-only ul li {
    position: relative;
}

.desktop-only ul li a {
    color: var(--header-text-white);
    padding: 10px 15px;
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.desktop-only ul li a:hover {
    color: var(--header-text-orange);
}

/* Submenu Styles */
.desktop-only ul li ul {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 100%;
    left: 0;
    background-color: var(--header-bg);
    min-width: 200px;
    z-index: 999;
}

.desktop-only ul li:hover > ul {
    display: block;
}

.desktop-only ul li ul li {
    width: 100%;
}

.desktop-only ul li ul li a {
    padding: 10px 15px;
    color: var(--header-text-white);
}

.desktop-only ul li ul li a:hover {
    background-color: var(--header-bg);
    color: var(--header-text-orange);
}

/* Responsive Design */

/* Mobile Styles */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    /* Mobile-specific overrides */
    .desktop-only {
        display: none;
    }

    .mobile-only {
        display: block;
    }

    header {
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
    }

    header nav.desktop-only {
        display: none; /* Hide the default desktop navigation */
    }

    .hamburger {
        display: flex;
    }

    .section {
        padding: 40px 10px;
    }
}

/* Desktop Reset Styles */
@media (min-width: 769px) {
    /* Reset sidebar and overlay when resizing to desktop */
    .toggle-sidebar:checked ~ .sidebar {
        right: -300px; /* Hide sidebar */
    }

    .toggle-sidebar:checked ~ .overlay {
        display: none;
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .desktop-only {
        display: block;
    }

    .mobile-only {
        display: none;
    }

    header nav.desktop-only {
        display: flex; /* Show the desktop navigation */
    }

    .hamburger {
        display: none; /* Hide the hamburger icon */
    }
}

/* Reset margins on first child of main-content to prevent collapsing */
.main-content > *:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
}
```

### **Explanation of Adjustments:**

1. **Separate Media Queries:**
   - **Mobile (`max-width: 768px`):** Styles specific to mobile view, hiding desktop navigation and showing the hamburger icon.
   - **Desktop (`min-width: 769px`):** Resets the sidebar and overlay regardless of the checkbox state, ensuring they remain hidden in desktop view. Also, it shows the desktop navigation and hides the hamburger icon.

2. **Adjusted `.main-content` Padding:**
   - The `padding-top` should match the header's height to prevent overlap. If your header's actual height is different, adjust the `padding-top` accordingly.
   - Example:

     ```css
     .main-content {
         padding-top: 60px; /* Adjust based on header's height */
         padding-left: 20px;
         padding-right: 20px;
         padding-bottom: 20px;
         margin: 0;
     }
     ```

3. **Resetting Margins on First Child:**
   - Prevents margin collapsing, which can introduce unintended gaps.

     ```css
     .main-content > *:first-child {
         margin-top: 0;
     }
     ```

4. **Ensuring No Extra Margins on `body` and `html`:**
   - Already handled in the reset styles.

5. **Consistency in Class Names:**
   - Ensure that the class names in your HTML (`header.php`) match those in your CSS (`style.css`).

